<bibRefCitation author="Kirejtshuk, A. G." pageId="77" pageNumber="78" pagination="56 - 63" refId="ref106236" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. (2011) A new genus of the family Nitidulidae (Polyphaga: Coleoptera) from Australia. Zoosystematica Rossica, 19 (2), 56 - 63." type="journal article" year="2011">Kirejtshuk 2011</bibRefCitation>
